# Ignore list for Salesforce metadata deployments

# Package directories we don't track
**/jsconfig.json
**/.eslintrc.json

# LWC test files
**/__tests__/**

# Profiles — managed via Permission Sets instead
**/profiles/**

# Community metadata (noisy, UI-managed)
**/experiences/**

# Scratch org settings
**/settings/Account.settings-meta.xml

# CI artifacts
scripts/output/
